## BUSINESS RULES
# Always consider these in development:

PRICING PSYCHOLOGY:
- Free (3 docs) → Single (€5) → 5-pack (€20) → 10-pack (€35)
- Highlight savings: €5 saved on 5-pack, €15 on 10-pack
- Position 5-pack as "Most Popular", 10-pack as "Best Value"

REVENUE OPTIMIZATION:
- Target: €35-70 monthly revenue per user (vs previous €15-30)
- Upsell triggers: Show packages when credits ≤ 1
- Purchase history: Track for personalized recommendations

TECHNICAL STANDARDS:
- Database: All personal data encrypted (AES-256-GCM)
- Retention: Documents auto-deleted after 24 hours
- Performance: Page load < 3 seconds mobile/desktop
- Mobile: Arabic RTL layout on all screen sizes

